TURNED AROUND AND CAME BACK

00:38:42.000 --> 00:38:46.000
AND WENT TO WORKING AGAIN,
AND THAT'S WHAT GRACE...

00:38:46.000 --> 00:38:48.000
MY FATHER KNEW THERE
WOULD BE A BETTER DAY

00:38:49.000 --> 00:38:51.000
BECAUSE THE GRACE WOULD HELP US.

00:38:51.000 --> 00:38:54.000
IF WE COULD JUST HAVE PATIENCE,
WE WOULD SEE A BETTER DAY.

