01:00:59.000 --> 01:01:13.000
* AND GRACE WILL LEAD ME HOME. *

01:01:29.000 --> 01:01:33.000
THOUGHTS UPON THE AFRICAN
 SLAVE TRADE, 1788.

01:01:33.000 --> 01:01:35.000
I HOPE IT WILL ALWAYS BE

01:01:35.000 --> 01:01:38.000
A SUBJECT OF HUMILIATING
 REFLECTION TO ME

01:01:38.000 --> 01:01:41.000
THAT I WAS ONCE
 AN ACTIVE INSTRUMENT

01:01:41.000 --> 01:01:44.000
IN A BUSINESS AT WHICH
 MY HEART NOW SHUDDERS.

01:01:44.000 --> 01:01:48.000
I FIRST SAW THE COAST OF GUINEA
 IN THE YEAR 1745

01:01:48.000 --> 01:01:50.000
AND TOOK MY LAST
 LEAVE OF IT IN 1754.

01:01:50.000 --> 01:01:53.000
I FITTED OUT
 FOR A FOURTH VOYAGE

01:01:53.000 --> 01:01:55.000
AND WAS UPON
 THE POINT OF SAILING

01:01:55.000 --> 01:01:58.000
WHEN I WAS ARRESTED
 BY A SUDDEN ILLNESS

01:01:58.000 --> 01:02:01.000
AND I RESIGNED THE SHIP
 TO ANOTHER CAPTAIN.

01:02:01.000 --> 01:02:06.000
THUS I WAS UNEXPECTEDLY FREED
 FROM THIS DISAGREEABLE SERVICE.

01:02:06.000 --> 01:02:09.000
DISAGREEABLE
 I HAD LONG FOUND IT

01:02:09.000 --> 01:02:13.000
BUT I THINK I SHOULD HAVE
 QUITTED IT SOONER

01:02:13.000 --> 01:02:18.000
HAD I CONSIDERED IT AS I DO
 NOW TO BE UNLAWFUL AND WRONG.

01:02:18.000 --> 01:02:22.000
BUT I NEVER HAD A SCRUPLE
 UPON THIS HEAD AT THE TIME

01:02:22.000 --> 01:02:27.000
NOR WAS SUCH A THOUGHT ONCE
 SUGGESTED TO ME BY ANY FRIEND.

01:02:27.000 --> 01:02:29.000
WHAT I DID, I DID IGNORANTLY

01:02:29.000 --> 01:02:31.000
CONSIDERING IT
 AS A LINE OF LIFE

01:02:31.000 --> 01:02:34.000
WHICH DIVINE PROVIDENCE
 HAD ALLOTTED ME

01:02:34.000 --> 01:02:37.000
AND HAVING NO CONCERN
 IN POINT OF CONSCIENCE

01:02:37.000 --> 01:02:40.000
BUT TO TREAT THE SLAVES
 WHILE UNDER MY CARE

01:02:40.000 --> 01:02:41.000
WITH AS MUCH HUMANITY

01:02:42.000 --> 01:02:44.000
AS A REGARD TO MY OWN
 SAFETY WOULD ADMIT.

01:02:44.000 --> 01:02:49.000
Burdon:
IT'S VERY HARD FOR US, I THINK,
TO UNDERSTAND THIS TODAY.

01:02:49.000 --> 01:02:53.000
FOR SOME TIME AFTER HIS
CONVERSION TO CHRISTIANITY

01:02:53.000 --> 01:02:56.000
HE CONTINUED IN THE SLAVE TRADE.

01:02:56.000 --> 01:02:59.000
HE DIDN'T SEE ANYTHING
FUNDAMENTALLY WRONG WITH IT

01:02:59.000 --> 01:03:02.000
AND IT WAS ONLY LATER IN LIFE

01:03:02.000 --> 01:03:05.000
WHEN HE WAS IN CONTACT
WITH WILLIAM WILBURFORCE

01:03:05.000 --> 01:03:10.000
THAT HE CAME OUT AS AN ADVOCATE
FOR ABOLISHING THE SLAVE TRADE

01:03:10.000 --> 01:03:14.000
AND GAVE A GREAT DEAL OF
INFORMATION AND AMMUNITION

01:03:14.000 --> 01:03:19.000
TO WILBURFORCE AND TO THE ROYAL
COMMISSION ON THE SLAVE TRADE.

01:03:19.000 --> 01:03:21.000
AND IT WAS JUST BEFORE HE DIED

01:03:21.000 --> 01:03:24.000
THAT THE ACT WENT
THROUGH PARLIAMENT.

01:03:24.000 --> 01:03:28.000
WILLIAM WILBURFORCE, WHO WAS
LOOKING FOR A PURPOSE IN LIFE

01:03:28.000 --> 01:03:30.000
LATCHED ONTO THIS CAUSE

01:03:30.000 --> 01:03:33.000
AND HE TOOK IT UP
IN THE HOUSE OF COMMONS

01:03:33.000 --> 01:03:36.000
AND FOUGHT FOR LEGISLATION
AGAINST SLAVERY

01:03:36.000 --> 01:03:38.000
FOR MANY YEARS THEREAFTER.

01:03:38.000 --> 01:03:41.000
BUT IT WAS MAINLY
THROUGH JOHN NEWTON

01:03:41.000 --> 01:03:44.000
TALKING ABOUT HIS EXPERIENCE
OF THE SLAVE TRADE

01:03:44.000 --> 01:03:48.000
THAT THE IMPORTANT AND
INFLUENTIAL PEOPLE IN LONDON

01:03:48.000 --> 01:03:51.000
CAME TO REALIZE
THAT IT WAS NOT GOOD.

01:03:51.000 --> 01:03:55.000
WITH OUR SHIPS, THE GREAT
 OBJECT IS TO BE FULL.

01:03:55.000 --> 01:03:59.000
THE CARGO OF A VESSEL OF
 100 TONS OR A LITTLE MORE

01:03:59.000 --> 01:04:03.000
IS CALCULATED TO PURCHASE
 FROM 220 TO 250 SLAVES

01:04:03.000 --> 01:04:08.000
FOR THE SLAVES LIE IN TWO ROWS,
 ONE ABOVE THE OTHER

01:04:08.000 --> 01:04:10.000
ON EACH SIDE OF THE SHIP

01:04:10.000 --> 01:04:14.000
CLOSE TO EACH OTHER,
 LIKE BOOKS UPON A SHELF.

01:04:14.000 --> 01:04:16.000
I HAVE KNOWN THEM SO CLOSE

01:04:16.000 --> 01:04:20.000
THAT THE SHELF WOULD NOT
 EASILY CONTAIN ONE MORE

01:04:20.000 --> 01:04:24.000
AND I HAVE KNOWN A WHITE MAN
 SENT DOWN AMONG THE MEN

01:04:24.000 --> 01:04:28.000
TO LAY THEM IN THESE ROWS
 TO THE GREATEST ADVANTAGE

01:04:28.000 --> 01:04:32.000
SO THAT AS LITTLE SPACE
 AS POSSIBLE MIGHT BE LOST.

01:04:32.000 --> 01:04:38.000
I WRITE FROM MEMORY, AFTER AN
 INTERVAL OF MORE THAN 30 YEARS.

01:04:38.000 --> 01:04:41.000
BUT AT THE SAME TIME, I BELIEVE

01:04:41.000 --> 01:04:44.000
MANY THINGS WHICH I SAW,
 HEARD AND FELT

01:04:44.000 --> 01:04:47.000
UPON THE COAST OF AFRICA

01:04:47.000 --> 01:04:50.000
ARE SO DEEPLY
 ENGRAVEN IN MY MEMORY

01:04:50.000 --> 01:04:55.000
THAT I CAN HARDLY FORGET,
 OR GREATLY MISTAKE THEM.

01:04:57.000 --> 01:05:01.000
Cooke:
I ALWAYS THINK THAT THE LINE,
"SAV'D A WRETCH LIKE ME"

01:05:01.000 --> 01:05:04.000
WAS NOT ONLY VERY TRUE
TO THE 18th CENTURY

01:05:04.000 --> 01:05:07.000
WHEN THAT SORT OF LANGUAGE
WOULD HAVE BEEN USED

01:05:07.000 --> 01:05:10.000
BUT HE REALLY SAW
HIMSELF AS A WRETCH.

01:05:10.000 --> 01:05:14.000
THE WAY HE DESCRIBED HIMSELF
AS BEING "VILER THAN ANYTHING"

01:05:14.000 --> 01:05:17.000
TIES IN WITH FEELINGS ABOUT
HIMSELF AS BEING A SINNER.

01:05:17.000 --> 01:05:21.000
TO BE INSCRIBED UPON MY DEATH:

01:05:21.000 --> 01:05:26.000
JOHN NEWTON, CLERK, ONCE
 AN INFIDEL AND LIBERTINE

01:05:26.000 --> 01:05:29.000
A SERVANT OF SLAVES IN AFRICA

01:05:29.000 --> 01:05:35.000
WAS, BY THE RICH MERCY OF OUR
 LORD AND SAVIOR, JESUS CHRIST

01:05:35.000 --> 01:05:38.000
PRESERVED, RESTORED, PARDONED

01:05:38.000 --> 01:05:41.000
AND APPOINTED
 TO PREACH THE FAITH

01:05:41.000 --> 01:05:44.000
HE HAD LONG LABORED TO DESTROY.

