THE SAME THING THAT HAS
BROUGHT ME THIS FAR

01:12:52.000 --> 01:12:55.000
IS GOING TO CARRY ME
THE REST OF THE WAY.

01:12:55.000 --> 01:12:57.000
I LIKE THAT.

