SEEMS TO HAVE BEEN SO BLESSED

01:13:00.000 --> 01:13:03.000
THAT IT'S HARD TO THINK
OF DANGERS, SNARES AND TOILS...

01:13:03.000 --> 01:13:07.000
OH, BUT I'M AFRAID THOSE
THINGS ARE IN EVERY LIFE

01:13:07.000 --> 01:13:10.000
WHATEVER IT MIGHT LOOK LIKE
FROM THE OUTSIDE.

01:13:10.000 --> 01:13:14.000
THERE ARE MOMENTS WHEN IT IS
VERY DIFFICULT, I THINK

01:13:14.000 --> 01:13:17.000
FOR MOST PEOPLE,
FOR WHATEVER REASONS

01:13:17.000 --> 01:13:22.000
FOR REASONS OF OUR OWN CREATION,
IMAGINED THINGS, I DON'T KNOW--

01:13:22.000 --> 01:13:27.000
BUT NOT EVERY MOMENT IS ONE OF
LIGHT AND ENERGY AND HAPPINESS.

