NO.

01:14:52.000 --> 01:14:55.000
A HYMN TAKES ON
A LIFE OF ITS OWN.

01:14:55.000 --> 01:14:56.000
OH, IT DOES.

01:14:56.000 --> 01:15:01.000
IT SHOWS WHAT A WONDERFUL
THING THIS IS.

